OL,3,CGrieving parents hope baby's death
OL,4,Cforces change after hospital neglect
OL,6,FThe mum of a one-year-old who died
OL,7,Ffrom sepsis after doctors dismissed
OL,8,Fhis symptoms as chickenpox says she
OL,9,Fwants his legacy to save other
OL,10,Fchildren.
OL,12,FHelen and Daniel Philliskirk's 16-
OL,13,Fmonth-old son James died in May 2022
OL,14,Fafter making several visits to
OL,15,FChildren's Hospital.
OL,17,FThe trust has admitted failings were
OL,18,Fmade and is now working with the
OL,19,Ffamily to make changes, including
OL,20,Fhiring a new specialist nurse.
