OL,4,Cforces change after hospital neglect
OL,6,FJames was taken to hospital on the
OL,7,Fadvice of his GP but medical
OL,8,Fprofessionals there were adamant he
OL,9,Fhad chickenpox, despite having already
OL,10,Fhad the disease in the weeks
OL,11,Fbeforehand.
OL,13,FJames was discharged but he continued
OL,14,Fto deterioriate, so his parents called
OL,15,F111 and were advised to take James
OL,16,Fback to the hospital.
