OL,3,CGrieving parents hope baby's death
OL,4,Cforces change after hospital neglect
OL,6,FMrs Philliskirk said despite
OL,7,Frepeatedly raising concerns that James
OL,8,Fmight be seriously ill, hospital staff
OL,9,Fremained convinced that he had
OL,10,Fchickenpox and a sore throat.
OL,12,F"He didn't move, he was 16 months but
OL,13,Fhe'd regressed to being a newborn baby.
OL,15,F"Everything I said to the doctor was
OL,16,Fshot down with a reason or an
OL,17,Fexplanation," she added.J"He'd never
OL,18,Fneeded medical treatment in the past
OL,19,Fbut within six hours we asked for help
OL,20,Ffour times, that is significant. There
OL,21,Fwas no weight given to that.
