OL,6,F"We weren't given any any safety
OL,7,Fnetting advice or told of anything we
OL,8,Fshould look out for."
OL,10,FMrs Philliskirk said they were told to
OL,11,Ftake James home with medication but
OL,12,Fthe next day he was found unresponsive
OL,13,Fin his cot by his father.
OL,15,F"My husband found him, picked him up
OL,16,Fand brought him into our room and
OL,17,Fscreamed 'he's gone.
OL,19,F"That's when our living nightmare
OL,20,Fstarted."
