OL,4,Cforces change after hospital neglect
OL,6,FA postmortem examination later
OL,7,Frevealed that James had sepsis brought
OL,8,Fon by a Strep A infection.
OL,10,FAn inquest into his death found
OL,11,Fneglect by the hospital contributed to
OL,12,Fhis death.
OL,14,FJames' parents now want to make
OL,15,Fchange, raise awareness of and
OL,16,Fencourage other parents to have the
OL,17,Fconfidence to ask for a second medical
OL,18,Fopinion if they feel their concerns
OL,19,Fare being dismissed.
