OL,6,FThey have also been working with the
OL,7,Fhospital to develop new practices,
OL,8,Fincluding the appointment of a new
OL,9,Flead sepsis nurse role.
OL,11,FMrs Philliskirk said: "It's the most
OL,12,Funimaginable pain and I'd never want
OL,13,Fanyone else to go through it. That has
OL,14,Fto be the driving force for sharing
OL,15,FJames' story.
OL,17,FShe said both her and her husband are
OL,18,F"doing everything we can to hold the
OL,19,Fhospital accountable and drive them to
OL,20,Fmake change."
