OL,6,FRuth Brown, Chief Executive of
OL,7,FSheffield Children's NHS Foundation
OL,8,FTrust, said: "We are truly sorry that
OL,9,Fthe care James received fell below the
OL,10,Fhigh standards we set ourselves and
OL,11,Fthat James, his family and loved ones
OL,12,Fshould have expected of us.
OL,14,F"Our internal investigation and the
OL,15,Finquest showed that there were
OL,16,Ffailings in James's care."
OL,18,FShe added: "Helen and Daniel have been
OL,19,Fboth courageous and generous with
OL,20,Ftheir time in helping us consider how
OL,21,Fwe take forward learning.
