OL,6,F"One part of our plans to address
OL,7,Fthese failings has been to undertake
OL,8,Ffurther work on sepsis, including the
OL,9,Fappointment to a new Lead Sepsis Nurse
OL,10,Frole.
OL,12,F"In creating the role, which Helen
OL,13,Fkindly took part in the interview
OL,14,Fprocess for, we looked at how we've
OL,15,Fmanaged sepsis in patients in the past
OL,16,Fand how we can continue to improve our
OL,17,Fpractice in the treatment of sepsis at
OL,18,FSheffield Children's in the future."
